                  whether your kitten was using a litter tray prior to adoption,
                  as this will allow you to select a litter tray and litter they
                  are already familiar with. If you're not sure, you can offer a
                  bit of a smorgasbord of litter trays to see which one they
                  naturally prefer to use. There are a variety of
                  <a href="https://storage.googleapis.com/litter-trays">litter
